The paper deals with satellite image classification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The authors also mention the use of data augmentation and feature engineering, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for image classification, which is a popular technique in graphics (cs.GR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
